{"tid":2293784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"納稅人一定要移民, 下一步係燒錢推高大灣區人工","createTime":"2020-11-20T13:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T07:06:30.000Z","uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"46a09c7b86e1fd8f812133cd9bc4af204a2c3925","tid":2293784,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T13:19:32.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥將於下周三（11月25日）公布新一份《施政報告》，《星島日報》引述消息報道，林鄭月娥將於發表《施政報告》時，宣布大灣區青年就業計劃。報道指，大灣區青年就業計劃，將支援數千香港青年到大灣區城市工作一年，涵蓋的行業包括科技、金融業等，設有年齡限制，每月工資可達1.5萬至2萬元，政府將會提供資助，惟實際細節尚未確定。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，有關計劃將以配對形式運作，騰訊 （00700） 等多家大企業已表示感興趣提供職位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://inews.hket.com/article/2807192/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2807192%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=4c6e5b48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://inews.hket.com/article/2807192/</a>"},{"pid":"d30431b63c0131e020c8d5d618c19f67e7c0c0cd","tid":2293784,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T13:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6be5577d55179889762c0e32e2c8e3386aab54","tid":2293784,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T15:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f770cb731677bcc56313e75dadfb06321cacfd84","tid":2293784,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T17:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfbaa3e7fe687311ab565af5d4aa6a3a96ee584","tid":2293784,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371d21458980b97960ebb981376eb5d293656e5f","tid":2293784,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets